# ShiftRegisterWorkPortfolio2022
Work portfolio assessment for year 11 mechatronics. Assignment 3 S2 Q3

DIRECTIONS FOR PLAY

Get up Serial Monitor for some encouragment and undertsanding of the code and game.
Once the arduino is powered a preloaded code will start a light sequence
The serial monitor will be serial printing "Waiting for user input" until a button is pressed
You will need to replicate the lights by pressing the parralel corresponding buttons and holding them down until the corresponding LED turns on.
if your input is correct the serial monitor will print "You got it right! Keep going üëèüéâ" 
else //aha
The serial monitor will print "You're wrong :(((" and flash all of the LEDs wice
shortly after the sequence will play again for your next try

